    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Leader. You are an inspiring commander and a master of battle tactics</p>\n<p><strong>Power Source:</strong> Martial. You have become an expert in tactics through endless hours of training and practice, personal determination, and your own sheer physical toughness.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Abilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Strength</li>\n<li>Intelligence</li>\n<li>Charisma</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Armour Proficiencies:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.GwsMGFG3ogxFrvmJ]{Cloth armor (basic clothing)}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.lnYMh2YvKedWTpCt]{Leather armor}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.kVD04UqK9Yx6GeRA]{Hide armor}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.LEPCRMtCimzvXr25]{Chainmail}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.7OaRnh5zUoThmChj]{Light Shield}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd4e.srd_rules.4vItzLTePIjC1MbI]{Simple Melee Weapons}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd4e.srd_rules.oRfaQkmDSxWMx5Ln]{Military Melee Weapons}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd4e.srd_rules.XKgEgbttyURcvqns]{Simple Ranged Weapons}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bonus to Defences:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>+1 Fort</li>\n<li>+1 Will&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong>&nbsp;[[12]] + Con Score</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points&nbsp;</strong><strong>per Level Gained:</strong> [[5]]</p>\n<p><strong>Base&nbsp;</strong><strong>Healing</strong><strong> Surges per Day:</strong> [[7]] + Con Mod</p>\n<p><strong>Skill Training:</strong> Choose three from the following list:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Athletics (Str)</li>\n<li>Diplomacy (Cha)</li>\n<li>Endurance (Con)</li>\n<li>Healing (Wis)</li>\n<li>History (Int)</li>\n<li>Intimidate (Cha)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Class Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Combat Leader</li>\n<li>Inspiring Word</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Choose one of the following Commanding Presence benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Inspiring Presence</li>\n<li>Tactical Presence</li>\n</ul>",
